Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:33.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:53.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:00.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:04.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.17,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:15.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:28.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:33.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:43.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試貼地性能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核對「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試地點性能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是富士崗賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擠滿了來看比賽的觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「高智能方程式」的富士崗預選賽將於明天舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各車隊現在正忙於整裝車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項賽事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為爭取在世界各地舉行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「高智能方程式」比賽的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界格蘭披治大賽的入場券
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受到注目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此項比賽勝出的頭三位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將有機會參加在北海道舉行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「全日本高智能方程式」選手權
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那項賽事勝出的頭三名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將能角逐世界格蘭披治大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在本賽事中勝出的最有實力隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵車隊的新條直輝選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正駕駛他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」GP進入賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟會展示出怎樣的比賽呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一話  決定命運的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔究竟在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在車檢前車子還未到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便趕不及出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美紀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你還有心情聽搖滾樂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是趕不及的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要闖出名堂的夢想就落空了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌張也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要盡了力就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該向阿牧學習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 總之請盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉 監督他們正趕來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是遲了入橫濱港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早巳知道會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早點運過來日本就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使趕得及車檢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能駕駛得了那部新車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連看都沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸和監督決定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用新車「阿斯拉達」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 大家都等得很心急了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才開得這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為颱風才遲了入港
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要向我發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏面叫「阿斯拉達」的車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我爸爸設計的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想駕駛看看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你已經十四歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有CF的駕駛執照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想試試駕駛它嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想成為賽車手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車一定能幫不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要做賽車手我寧願駕電單車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟從電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便任何人都能駕駛的車一點都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個卻不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要移動把手 車子就任你操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向把你交託給我的你爸爸交待?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常 所有數值顯示無問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起步的速度太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強系統反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 SWITICH 0N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強 0.0l3 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0.0l2才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試定風翼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定風翼的效果正如程式所示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵「SUPERION」的狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調整好後應該可再快兩秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進修理站作最後的調整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 新條先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在彎角用定風翼時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子會「洗汰」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 新條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是歐洲冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新車的調整很了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生 請說幾句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生 你本是歐洲冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可否說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會突然轉參加CF呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個由我來答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最受注目的CF賽車的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那頂點為目標的我們的車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以冠軍為為目標的他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可說是一拍即合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有他的天才駕駛技術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上我們車隊的高科技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對有足夠實力問鼎世界大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼新條先生的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界格蘭披治大賽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是那個鋪排已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說眼中已沒有對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼但除了新條先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩個能入選
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本選手權的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為會是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於追到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經發現「阿斯拉達」 開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要截住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷得真嚴重!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是爸爸造的車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電單車撞損得很厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我是問你有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷了一下膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟想幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車! 他們想吊走那車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把車…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部車就是我們車隊的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能讓你們破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們奔向世界的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們究竟是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些遲點再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把車子帶到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一次駕駛CF吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起車子 車田叔的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子比我的身體更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是車匙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等趕及車檢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把車送去後就回來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座椅怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微踩一下油門便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車子怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高速可去到時速250公里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那車子怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是CF
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這種地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有型～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時速已經200公里了 還要加速嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無線電通訊器在哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請減速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是導航系統「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是無線電嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我沒空和電腦談了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 駕駛員的技術真有夠差的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能運用到我30％的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手還未成熟  真囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情況後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要搶走「阿斯拉達」?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在「阿斯拉達」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千均一發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人駕駛它到安全的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子運動神經很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必會沒事的 想不到這麼快便成搶奪對像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 走快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才可以提升速度?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」現在正為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高速度而調整中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你選的路線要修改下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是說這種話的時候嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若修改路線有困難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請按一號按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號…是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種機能的話就早點出聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是剛剛才收到你的詢問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去富士崗賽道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才發出的雷達衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能確認位置的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發出了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想完全有效地活用這部車的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便要好好瞭解一下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在崖蓬穿過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動三號按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使車身打側
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 三號按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動抽氣系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我爸爸製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見這麼厲害的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界上是數一數二的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是推進器的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要推動在你身旁的推進器手把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能將引擎的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間增加1．7倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這段時間不能持久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若超過時限 引擎將會因過熱而爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 安全渡過後再慢慢聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逃離這裏才證明你是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多久就到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣減速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦? 「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去車身會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若可以的話一早便做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是問你逃離這兒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把握狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊要關頭 卻一點也幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 爸爸 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進器啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎進入臨界點 開始倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧! 「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 隼人把「阿斯拉達」…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該差不多時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 還未到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 要平安到達啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿牧 不要理那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰隊好像很慌張似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新車不知有否送來?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新車?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小車隊罷了 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個 一定是隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是CF嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能理解你的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說真是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把你送到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是管生車隊的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲紋和角膜已被我記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你以外的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能開動這部車的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修改紀錄系統需要一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是預選賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們能成為好拍擋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

